<h1>Instructions</h1>
<p>The Food Foraging Fiesta! will help you keep</p>
<p>track of your food storage inventory, and lest </p>
<p>you know what you should add.</p><br>

<p>1. Set up your preferences</p>
<p>2. Enter your current inventory</p>
<p>3. Use suggested shopping list to purchase </p>
<p>needed items.</p>
<p>4. Add items to inventory in the store or </p>
<p>when stocking up.</p>
<p>5. Remove items from inventory as they are used.</p><br>

<p>• The current inventory can be viewed.</p>
<p>• The recommended inventory can be </p>
<p>adapted for your family.</p>
<p>• The type of units can be selected per item.</p>
<p>• Deluxe Storage includes spices and other </p>
<p>items to improve meals.</p>
<p>• Basic Storage is food necessary for survival.</p>
<p>• Selecting “Infants” will add diapers, etc.</p>
